<p>When you use the services for transportation or delivery, we collect precise location data about the trip from the ExpressDrive app used by the Drivers and Riders. If you permit the ExpressDrive apps to access location services through the permission system used by your mobile operating system (“platform”), we may also collect the precise location of your device when the app is running in the foreground or background. We may also derive your approximate location from your IP address.</p>

<h2>Contacts Information:</h2>
<p>If you permit the ExpressDrive apps to access the address book on your device through the permission system used by your mobile platform, we may access and store names and contact information from your address book to facilitate social interactions through our Services and for other purposes described in this Statement or at the time of consent or collection.</p>
